 <h3 class="title"><a href="node/1733#comment-21146" class="active">MIT&#039;s Lifelong Kindergarten</a></h3>
 <div class="content"><p >MIT has a research program going on called <a href="http://llk.media.mit.edu/projects.php?id=783">Scratch</a>, a programming language for children.  It's a bit like Flash, with a much more user-friendly GUI.</p>
<p >They're also developing tutorial videos for using the system <a href="http://llk.media.mit.edu/projects.php?id=1774">here</a>.</p>
